oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Performance - The Bankesters - 2015-11-07
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by the Bankesters as part of the Bluegrass and Beyond program from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on November 7, 2015. Third performer of four. Presented by the Crump family and Cotton Music. Honoring George A. and Marjorie S. Crump.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: The Bankesters;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Introduced by Jim Hurst. Performances include; Get Right Or Get Left -- Love Has Wheels -- Unidentified Song -- Looking Forward To Looking Back -- Glory Bound -- Unidentified Instrumental -- Oh, Atlanta -- Interview Segment -- Love, Don't Give Up On Me -- When God Dips His Pen Of Love In My Heart -- Something Worth Waiting For -- Where I Am -- I Gotta Have You -- Count On Me -- Gypsy Jubilee -- Shine - Cups (When I'm Gone).
